Loops
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-Loops are a fundamental concept in programming and are used to repeat a block of code multiple times.

-They are essential for tasks that require repetitive actions or operations.

------------------
Why?
------------------

-Automation of Repetitive Tasks

-Efficiency

-Dynamic and Scalable Code

-Code Simplification

------------------
Types
------------------

    --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    1.Kotlin For Loop:
    --------------------------------------------------------------------------------

     -Used to iterate over a range, collection, array, or anything that provides an iterator.

         Syntax
         ------------
          for (condition) {
                   // code block to be executed
                 }

          fun main() {
              for (i in 1..10) {
                  println(i)
              }
          }
    ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    2.Kotlin While Loop
    ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    -The while loop loops through a block of code as long as a specified condition is true:

        Syntax
        ----------------------------------
        while (condition) {
          // code block to be executed
        }

        Example
        ----------------------------------
        fun main(){
            var i = 0
                while (i < 5) {
                  println(i)
                  i++
                }
        }
    ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    3.Kotlin Do..While Loop
    ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
      The do..while loop is a variant of the while loop. This loop will execute the code block once,

      before checking if the condition is true, then it will repeat the loop as long as the condition is true.

          Syntax
          ------------------------------------
          do {
            // code block to be executed
          }
          while (condition);


          example
          ------------------------------------
          fun main(){
            var i:0
            do{
                println(i)
                i++
            }while(i<5)
          }